metadata.name: Existence
metadata.description: "The Existence" is a thought-provoking piece that’s inspired by the human experience. The trippy, colorful wave print in the background, with its swirling patterns and intriguing symbols, provides a visual representation of the constant ebb and flow of existence. The black hole in the purple being’s chest symbolizes the complexity and depth of our emotions and the search for meaning in our lives. Whether you put it in your digital wallet or on your wall, this art is a real head-turner.
